Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.80,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ điều chỉnh cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll help, too, of course!}Chị cũng giúp nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.98,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{So will Hayakawa-san.}Và Hayakawa nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.17,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I guess I don't mind pitching in...}À thì... em cũng không phiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Work hard to win that most promising \Nhire award, Shinozaki-san!}Cố gắng hết sức để nhắm đến\N giải thưởng nào, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:55.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll do just that! Let's all go \Nto that tropical resort together!}Em sẽ cố hết sức! Mọi người hãy cùng nhau đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.57,Main,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,{So that's why you're so fired up.}Đó là lý do cậu hào hứng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I wanna live up to their expectations!}Phải đáp lại kì vọng của mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:09.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That said, I still don't have a concrete \Nidea for my proposal yet...}Cơ mà vẫn chưa có kế hoạch rõ ràng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What about you, Yamagishi-kun?}Còn cậu, Yamagishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.04,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Not interested. Too big a pain.}Không hứng thú. Phiền lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:21.17,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs18\b1\shad0\c&H191421&\3c&HA0E5F6&\pos(178.667,277.334)\frz9.06}{Supreme Opulence!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:21.17,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\shad0\bord1\c&H121726&\3c&HF0F0F0&\pos(415,295)}{Luxury Resort}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.65,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What about the luxury resort?}Còn nghỉ dưỡng cao cấp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.22,Main - Top,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,{Even less interested.}Càng không hứng thú.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:21.17,Main - Top,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,Với cả mấy người bên PR...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.62,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Could you pwease help wif dis?}Giúp anh được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.55,Main,Yagimishi(M),0,0,0,,{Don't wanna.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.89,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yuri-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.03,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,Masa-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.14,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Bluh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.32,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I doubt I'd enjoy it at all.}Thế này nghỉ dưỡng sao nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I guess I'm sorry?}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.64,Main,Yamigishi(M),0,0,0,,{You really hit the jackpot, \Nthough, Zakishino...}Còn cậu thì hên ghê, Zakishino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.88,Main,Yamigishi(M),0,0,0,,{You got a 5-star senpai with a 5-star boss to boot!}Có toàn hàng siêu hiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Could you not treat the people in my \Ndepartment like gacha characters?}Đừng xem con người là nhân vật gacha nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.95,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fnArial\b1\shad0\c&H7D6F86&\3c&HB6ECFA&\pos(169.334,50)}{Employment\NAgent}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.95,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Maybe I oughta contact a job agent and \Nsee about trying a reset marathon...}Có lẽ tớ nên tìm một công ty khác và chuyển việc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.69,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I'm telling you, it tasted amazing.}Phải đó, tuyệt lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.83,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Speak of the devil...}Vừa mới nhắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.83,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{There's 5-star senpai.}Đàn chị siêu hiếm kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.78,Main,Yamakawa,0,0,0,,{And there's no limit!}Và không giới hạn luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.66,Main,Yamagishi (F),0,0,0,,{There's not?!}Không luôn á?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.19,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Plus, the interior is so cute.}Với cả bên trong cũng dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.02,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{We're both rookies and we make \Nthe same money, but look at the difference!}Hai ta đều là lính mới, cùng mức\Nlương mà sao khác biệt vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.84,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Is life just pure RNG?!}Cuộc đời dựa hoàn toàn vào may rủi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.48,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{With a senpai like that I'd be \Nwilling to work Monday to Friday}Với đàn chị siêu hiếm đó thì tớ\N nguyện đi làm tới thứ 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:15.08,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{for nine hours a day, \Nminus one hour for lunch, too!}9 tiếng 1 ngày, giải lao 1 tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You should be able to do that anyway.}Cái đó ai chả làm được!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.10,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Be real with me. How are \Nthings going, Zakishino?}Cơ mà chú nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{With what?}Nghĩ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.23,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,Đừng giả ngu.{Don't play dumb.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.48,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{With you and Katase-paisen!}Nghĩ sao về chị Katase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.15,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I mean, she came to check on you \Nat your house...}Chị ấy đã từng đến nhà thăm bệnh rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:33.74,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{And you went on a trip \Ntogether, right? Right? Right?}Cả hai cùng đi du lịch chung nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.29,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nothing... happened...}Không có gì... xảy ra cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:45.60,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Unbelievable. What, you see \Nthose boobs and just feel nothing?}Cái gì cơ... Không cảm nhận được bộ ngực đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Don't talk so bluntly about boobs!}Đừng có nói đến ngực!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I mean...}T-Thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I guess I can't say it's been \Nabsolutely nothing.}Không hẳn là không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:57.64,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Holy crap, the deed's already done?!}Vậy là có gì rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.16,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Give him back! I want \Nmy pure-hearted Zakishino back!}Trả lại đây! Trả đàn chị trong sáng lại đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm still pure, actually!}Vẫn còn trong sáng lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.07,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Five minutes left of lunch.}Nghỉ trưa còn 5 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:11.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh... you're Kurusu-san, right?}Kurusu nhỉ?
