Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.70,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{That's Kurusu Akari from Development Group 1!}Kurusu Akari từ nhóm phát triển số 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:18.18,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Watch yourself, Zakishino!}Cẩn thận đó Zakishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.81,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{She was hand-picked \Nas the rising star of Group 1}Cô ta là ngôi sao của nhóm 1 đó
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.34,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{by their charismatic, high-minded chief!}bậc thầy trí tuệ, niềm tự hào của nhóm 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:30.72,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{She's got the hottest rep out of anyone \Nwho joined up the same year as us...}Là lính mới nổi bật nhất trong đám chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:35.97,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{And she's favored to win \Nthe most promising rookie contest!}Và cũng được ưu ái giành \Nchiến thắng cuộc thi lần này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.40,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Time should be productive, not wasted...}Thời gian không được lãng phí.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.35,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{If you want to progress to the next stage.}Nếu muốn tiến tới giai đoạn tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.94,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That does sound high-minded!}Nghe trí tuệ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.78,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{You were also discussing... breasts.}Vừa rồi... hai người bàn về ngực nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.24,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{That's sexual harassment.}Đó là quấy rối đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.53,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're right, it is.}Đúng là thế nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:58.70,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Not when it comes to Zakishino \Nand Senpai. They're mutually in love.}Zakishiro và đàn chị thì không sao. \NHai người đang yêu nhau mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yamagishi-kun?!}Yamagishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.77,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{The partner is... his senpai?}Đối phương... là đàn chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.54,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{She's abusing her authority, then?}Lạm quyền à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wha?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.75,Main,Kurus,0,0,0,,{Exploiting her power.}Lợi dụng quyền lực.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai isn't—}Chị ấy không--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:11.51,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Chill out, Zakishino. Leave this to me.}Bình tĩnh Zakishino, cứ để tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.01,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{This ain't no abuse.}Không phải lạm quyền.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:15.60,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Because the two of them are going out!}Mà bọn họ đang hẹn hò.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Also not true!}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.81,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Workplace romance... Can't understand.}Tình cảm công sở, thật khó hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.77,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{We don't provide matchmaking services here.}Chúng ta không có cung cấp dịch vụ mai mối.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:29.16,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Yet, according to surveys, more than a quarter \Nof married couples met at work.}Nhưng theo khảo sát thì 1/4 cặp đôi \Ngặp và kết hôn ở môi trường làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.28,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{It's totally natural.}Hoàn toàn bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Easy, now...}Thôi nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.03,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,Kurusu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.71,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{\an8}{This is rare. You normally \Ndon't stick around in the break room.}Hiếm thấy em nghỉ đến sát giờ thế này đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.71,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(175,0)\p1\c&HF2F7F6&\bord0\shad0\blur2\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(106,292)}m 0 0 l 170 0 l 170 75 l 0 75
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.71,sign_4975_56_Days_Earlier,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(175,0)\fscx100\fscy140\bord0\q2\fs18\pos(106,292)}{Development Group 1 Chief\N}{\fs20\fscy180}{Takatsukasa Shinobu}Quản lý nhóm 1\N Takatsukasa Shinobu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:47.08,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Director Takatsukasa...}Quản lý Takatsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:52.16,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Waste of time... won't be able \Nto get back to work right away...}Phí thời gian... sẽ không thể quay lại làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:56.05,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it. \NYou've still got four minutes.}Đừng lo, vẫn còn 4 phút mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.18,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{The crucial thing is being able to \Nswitch your state of mind around.}Quan trọng là có thể chuyển đổi trạng thái ngay lập tức.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.36,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Mistakes and regrets will be fuel \Nto carry you to the next stage.}Sai lầm và hối hận sẽ\N dẫn chúng ta đến giai đoạn tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.31,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:07.55,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{She really is high-minded, \Nand charismatic, that chief...}Không hổ là một quản lý của nhân viên giỏi nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.86,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{S-So bright!}T-Toả sáng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:13.82,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{You're Shinozaki-kun from Dev Group 2, yes?}Em là Shinozaki ở nhóm phát triển số 2 nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.94,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Your manager and I joined \Nthe company at the same time.}Quản lý của em và tôi vào công ty cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.58,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I make it a point to keep up \Nwith Group 2's new hires.}Tôi đã luôn theo dõi lính mới của nhóm 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:24.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You and Manager? That'd mean...}Chị và quản lý... Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.58,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Isn't that amazing?}Tuyệt nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.46,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I feel bad for the other rookies.}Em thấy tệ cho những người vào cùng hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's who I felt bad for!}Người tội nghiệp xuất hiện rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:33.92,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Something wrong?}Có chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.47,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, nothing!}À không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.93,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Akina and I have been friendly rivals}Akina và chị là đối thủ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.72,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{who've spurred each other on to \Ngreater heights, even back then.}luôn hỗ trợ nhau để đạt được vị trí cao hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:44.35,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{That said, he's always proven \Nto be more talented...}Nói vậy chứ anh ấy có thực lực áp đảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.35,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{His proposal blew mine away.}Đề xuất kế hoạch đó khiến chị thất bại hoàn toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:49.10,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,0)\fs16\b1\fnArial\shad0\an8\c&H4F46E3&\3c&HFCFCFF&\i1\move(268,66,234,66)}{Celebrating Product\NDevelopment Group 2's Major Hit}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.10,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{And the product that came from it was a hit—}Và sản phẩm đó là một bước đột phá--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:53.78,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I've had my hands full \Njust trying to catch up to him.}Chị đã dùng hết sức để đuổi theo anh ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:58.30,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{But before I realized it, I had been promoted \Nfaster than anyone in company history.}Nhưng trước khi kịp nhận ra, chị đã trở thành \Nngười lên chức nhanh nhất công ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.74,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{And he's stopped \Nmaking as many obvious waves...}Còn anh ấy đã ngừng tạo ra những làn sóng mới...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:04.37,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{But I still can't forget it.}Nhưng chị vẫn không quên.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:09.83,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Those days when competing with him \Nraised both of our games higher and higher...}Những ngày đấu với anh ấy để\N cả hai cùng phát triển cao hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:12.63,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{And I've realized something.}Và chị đã nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.26,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I need him!}Chị cần anh ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.76,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I've already spoken to the president about it.}Chị cũng đã yêu cầu giám đốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.03,Flashback,President,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:26.12,Flashback,President,0,0,0,,{Well, if Kurusu-kun can win \Nthe most promising rookie competition,}Nếu cô có thể đưa Kurusu thắng giải tân binh lần này,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.49,Flashback,President,0,0,0,,{I'll consider transferring Akina-kun.}thì tôi sẽ thuyên chuyển Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:35.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If I lose the contest... \Nthe manager's going to get transferred?!}Nếu thua... thì anh ấy sẽ chuyển qua kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:35.03,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(156,16)\an8\b1\fs18\c&H000000&\3c&HFAFEFF&\4c&HFCE4D6&}{Development Group 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:35.03,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\b1\fs18\c&H000000&\3c&HFAFEFF&\4c&HDAD7FC&\pos(486,16)}{Development Group 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.03,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, no!}Ôi không!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.72,Main,Yamagishi(M)),0,0,0,,{Since when did he become the heroine?}Từ khi nào thành nữ chính vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Cut that out! That's just gonna \Nconfuse me more!}Khoan đã! Tớ cũng đang rối lắm đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.99,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{I thought it'd be unfair if you didn't know.}Chị nghĩ không công bằng nếu không nói gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:48.56,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{Granted, we're bound to win... \Nso don't feel too torn up about it.}Mà thôi, bọn chị sẽ giành chiến thắng nên đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.00,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{It's time, Kurusu.}Đi thôi Kurusu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.54,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.88,Main,Shizozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait a second!}Khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.67,Main,Shizozaki,0,0,0,,{You might need him,}Có thể chị cần anh ấy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:56.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{but I don't intend on handing our manager over.}nhưng bọn em không định giao ra đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.80,Main,Shizozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm going to win that \Nmost promising rookie award.}Em sẽ chiến thắng giải tân binh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.55,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's a good look in your eye.}Ánh mắt được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.30,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,Ánh mắt tiến đến giai đoạn tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:06.93,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{That said...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:10.94,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{The competition... I won't lose to anyone.}Cuộc thi tân binh... tôi sẽ chiến thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.69,Main,Kurusu,0,0,0,,{I'll win most promising rookie.}Tôi sẽ là người vô địch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.19,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{We're taking this.}Bọn này sẽ chiến thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.57,Main,Takatsukasa,0,0,0,,{And Kurusu will go on to aim \Nfor even greater heights.}Và Kurusu sẽ nhắm đến vị trí cao hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:31.23,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Well, that got real competitive \Nall of a sudden!}Tự nhiên thành phim chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:31.95,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.80,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Fantastic!}Ảo thật đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.71,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{That was fantastic, Shinozaki-kun!}Vừa rồi em tuyệt lắm, Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:42.78,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{A heated battle between subordinates, \Non behalf of their bosses!}Một trận chiến giữa các tân binh\N thay mặt cho các quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.47,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{So nice!}Tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.11,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Em cũng nên thế, chiến đấu vì anh!{You should fight, too, Yamagishi-kun! For me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.23,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Ishiyama-san, no one wants you, so I can't.}Ishiyama, không ai cần anh nên chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:55.61,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Wow, what a turn of events \Nfor the rookie contest!}Chà, cuộc thi tân binh lần này hào hứng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.13,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Are you even listening?}Anh có nghe em không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:58.83,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{A battle over me!}Trận chiến đặt cược anh thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:11:59.86,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{No, seriously...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.27,Main - Top,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Good luck out there, Yamagishi-kun!}Cố lên Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:00.91,Main - Top,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{There's no fight here.}Không có cuộc chiến nào ở đây cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The new hire contest...}Cuộc thi tân binh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:01.39,Main - Top,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Good luck!}Chúc may mắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:01.93,Main - Top,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{I don't need encouragement.}Em không cần chúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.35,Main - Top,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{You do!}Cần chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:02.80,Main - Top,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.50,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I can't lose, no matter what!}Mình không thể thua được.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.50,Main - Top,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Good luck!}Chúc may mắn!
