Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Manager, about my project \Nfor the competition...}Quản lý, về kế hoạch cho cuộc thi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.75,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Look at that!}Nhìn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.96,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{That tea stalk is standing up!}Lá trà đang đứng thẳng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I bet that's a good sign for something!}Có vẻ là chuyện tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.92,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I hope so. Having green tea \Nevery once in a while is nice, too.}Phải nhỉ, uống trà đúng là tuyệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure is!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So carefree...}Thoải mái dữ vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I hope you'll play with me a whole lot!}Chơi với chị nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.95,Main,Kids+Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
