Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.17,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{So many toys!}Nhiều đồ chơi quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.33,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{I know this!}Tớ biết con này!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.74,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\an8}{They're cute.}Dễ thương ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:47.66,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{Be sure to thank the nice people for the toys!}Hãy cảm ơn các anh chị nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.49,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Thank you!}Cảm ơn anh chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.34,Main,Girl A,0,0,0,,{Would you like to accompany me to the ball?}Có muốn cùng tớ đến buổi khiêu vũ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.72,Main,Girl I,0,0,0,,{Me, too!}Tớ nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:56.25,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Then let's all dance together.}Hãy nhảy múa cùng nhau nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.49,Main,Girl U,0,0,0,,{Onee-chan, draw Kyapicure!}Chị vẽ Kyapicure đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.31,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,{Nice art!}Đẹp quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.04,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.40,Main,Girl E,0,0,0,,{I want Meowjiro!}Em muốn Nyanjiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.97,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay, sure! I'll do my best!}Rồi rồi! Chị sẽ vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:05.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{The kids seem really thrilled.}Đám trẻ có vẻ vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I didn't know we oversaw \Nproduct tests like this.}Không ngờ sản phẩm thử nghiệm\N lại được dùng làm thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We see how they play with them, \Nand make adjustments based on that.}Chúng ta sẽ quan sát thực tế và điều chỉnh lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We don't get many chances for this, \Nso get as much research done as you can.}Hiếm lắm mới có cơ hội nên hãy quan sát kĩ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It might help with your contest.}Có thể sẽ giúp cho cuộc thi của em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.15,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The contest, huh...}Cuộc thi à...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.37,Flashback,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Did you tell Senpai?}Cậu có nói với chị ấy chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:29.28,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't want her to worry, though...}Tớ không muốn chị ấy lo lắng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:33.35,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So I haven't told her about Manager yet.}Và cuối cùng mình vẫn chưa nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have to say...}Phải nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.10,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Hey, come over here!}Nè, lại đây đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What should we play?}Chúng ta chơi gì nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.10,Main,Shiori?,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:42.42,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She's so motherly!}Chị ấy toả ra hào quang người mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The kids are drawn to her effortlessly...}Không làm gì nhưng hút con nít ghê thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Downright Madonna-like!}Cứ như thánh mẫu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But more than that...}Quan trọng hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, honey.}Mừng anh trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wife factor...}Người vợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{High!}Phê!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Do your job.}Làm việc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-I know!}Biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.67,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, what do you guys wanna play?}Mấy bé muốn chơi gì nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.86,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Um, let me think..}Để xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{With this? Or maybe this?}Cái này hả? Hay cái này?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He broke the ice so easily.}Dễ dàng làm thân như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's Shinozaki-san. \NHe's such a capable kohai.}Không hổ là Shinozaki, đàn em đa năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And then there's...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{how paternal he is!}sao toả ra hào quang người cha thế kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All the kids he's \Ninteracting with are smiling...}Đám trẻ cũng bị ảnh hưởng bởi nụ cười đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's like he's some kind of all-father!}Cứ như người cha toàn năng ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And more than that...}Và hơn thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, honey.}Mừng em trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Husband factor...}Người chồng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{High!}Phê!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.24,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Stare...}Nhìn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Uh, well...}Ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What should we do to play?!}C-Chúng ta chơi trò gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.48,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Come on, Tomo-kun! Don't pull!}Tomo này, đừng có kéo nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.14,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{You're gonna rip Meowtaro!}Cậu sẽ xé rách nyantaro đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.04,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Then, you let go, Marin!}Vậy cậu thả ra trước đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's play nice together.}Hãy chơi cùng nhau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I've got another Meowtaro right here.}Anh còn một Nyantaro nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:51.16,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{I don't wanna play with some dumb doll.}Em không thích chơi mấy con thú bông ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:55.16,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{But she's always playing \Nwith them all by herself!}Nhỏ này lúc nào cũng toàn chơi với chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You noticed that, huh?\NDo you want to play with her?}Em quan sát kĩ ghê. Muốn chơi cùng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:14:59.41,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Wha...}Cái...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.17,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Who'd wanna play with Marin?!}Ai thèm chơi cùng Marin chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.21,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Did that hurt, Meowtaro?}Đau không Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There, there...}Ngoan ngoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:09.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's okay now. He's not hurt.}Em nó không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you usually play alone?}Em hay chơi một mình hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.93,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Yeah. My friends are the dolls.}Vâng, bạn của Marin là búp bê.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:21.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I see. But I'd like you to play \Nwith us, too, Marin-chan.}Vậy à? Nhưng bọn chị muốn chơi cùng em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.94,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Then, let's play house!}Vậy chơi trò gia đình đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.94,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{House?}Gia đình?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.44,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Onii-chan, you're the daddy.}Anh là papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.95,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Shinozaki-san's the daddy...}Papa Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.87,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{And you, Onee-chan...}Còn chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.08,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Th-The way this is going...}K-Không có lẽ..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.58,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Onee-chan, you're mommy!}Chị là mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Mommy?}Mẹ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.33,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Yeah! He's daddy and you're mommy!}Anh là papa còn chị là mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:48.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Even if we're just playing... he's my kohai...}Chỉ là trò chơi thôi nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.68,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{No! Mommy doesn't call daddy her kohai!}Không! Phải gọi tên ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Th-Then...}V-Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Takuma-san.}Takuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Shiori-san.}Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.52,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Yay! Daddy! Mommy!}Papa! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:07.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's like a vision of the future!}Viễn cảnh tương lai sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No! The child is supposed to be \Nthe star when you play house!}Không được! Khi chơi trò này thì trung tâm là trẻ em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.90,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Onee-chan...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.49,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{You'll be kitty!}Chị sẽ là con mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.24,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{And I'll be mommy. And you're kitty!}Còn em là mama, chị là con mèo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.91,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm... a kitty?}Mình... là con mèo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.25,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I guess Senpai seems like a cat to kids, too.}Có vẻ em ấy nghĩ chị là mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:30.54,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A cat... I mean, that is \Na member of the family, but...}Mèo... đúng là có thành viên đó thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.88,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So I'm an animal, not a human...}Mình là thú nuôi sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:36.06,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Daddy, dinner is ready!}Papa, bữa tối xong rồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.14,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{There, there.}Ngoan ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.66,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Do you want to eat, too, kitty?}Em có muốn ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.14,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{In that case...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.77,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Sit on Daddy's lap.}Ngồi lên đùi papa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:53.59,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{S-S-Sit... on Daddy's lap?!}N-N-Ngồi lên đùi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.64,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{No!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.41,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{You have to sit for real!}Mau ngồi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.33,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{If you don't wanna do that, then lie on it.}Nếu không muốn thì nằm cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Like lie down?! In his lap?!}Nằm á? Nằm lên đùi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That'd be sexual harassment \Nand abuse of authority!}Vừa là quấy rối và lạm quyền luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Serious charges!}Tội nghiêm trọng đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:16.43,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But the child is the star \Nwhen you play house...}Nhưng trẻ em là trung tâm khi chơi trò gia đình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.59,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I should...}Mình phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{S-Senpai?!}C-Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.85,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{There you go. Good girl.}Ngoan lắm ngoan lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.02,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Give the kitty pats, Daddy.}Papa cũng xoa đầu đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Patting her while lying around?!}Xoa đầu trong khi chị ấy đang nằm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:37.11,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Those are couple activities! In broad \Ndaylight, in front of small children?!}Làm trò này trước mặt trẻ em sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:40.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But Senpai's a cat right now...}Nhưng chị ấy đang là mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But I'm a cat right now...}Nhưng mình đang là mèo mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:50.07,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{G-Good girl...}N-Ngoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:55.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe life as a cat... wouldn't be so bad.}Làm mèo... cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.72,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Okay, your food is here, kitty.}Rồi, thức ăn nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:03.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Eating off the floor... \Nbut I'm a cat... I'm a cat.}Ăn dưới sàn sao? Mình là mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:07.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Senpai is crawling around on the ground...}Chị ấy đang bò dưới sàn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:09.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yum-meow!}Ngon quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.82,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{We're done eating, \Nso let's have a picnic in the sandbox!}Ăn xong thì đi picnic thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.84,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{But there's a shark inside, so be careful.}Bên trong có cá mập nên cẩn thận nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A shark at a picnic?}Cá mập khi đi dã ngoại á?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Be careful now, Mommy.}Cẩn thận nhé Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.83,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{I'm Mommy!}Em là Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{R-Right! Sorry!}À quên!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, Shinozaki-san...}Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:38.22,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{The castle I made with Daddy and Kitty...}Lâu đài làm với papa và mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:41.24,Main,tomo,0,0,0,,{He's not a daddy, and she's not a cat!}Anh ta không phải papa và chị ấy không phải mèo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.04,Main,tomo,0,0,0,,{And there's no sharks, either!}Cũng chẳng có cá mập nào cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sharks...?}Cá mập?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Were you watching the whole time?}Em quan sát nãy giờ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.23,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{H-Hell no!}Còn lâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.98,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Why would I look at Marin?}Mắc gì quan sát Marin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.84,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Tomo-kun!}Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san!}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:19:00.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If you like a girl, be nice to her.}Nếu em thích ai đó thì hãy dịu dàng với họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.95,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Sorry... you still mad?}Cậu... còn giận hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.75,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{I guess.}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:15.61,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{I really am sorry. Let's remake it...}Tớ xin lỗi. Cùng làm lại nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.26,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{And then can I play with you?}Và tớ chơi cùng cậu được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.49,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{I guess that's fine.}Cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:26.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So, when we play house, who will Tomo-kun be?}Vậy thì hãy chơi tiếo thôi. Tomo sẽ đóng vai gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.61,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{Tomo-kun is...}Tomo là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.10,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{The shark.}Cá mập.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.31,Main,Others,0,0,0,,{The shark?!}Cá mập?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:34.15,Main,Marin,0,0,0,,{He's mean, so he has to be \Nthe shark that I hate.}Cậu ấy hay bắt nạt em, nên là cá mập, em ghét.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:38.40,Main,Tomo,0,0,0,,{Sh-Shark... the one she hates...}C-Cá mập... bị ghét...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.91,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye!}Tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.04,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Thank you!}Cảm ơn các anh chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.79,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{Come again!}Hãy đến chơi nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:47.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Bye-bye!}Tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Hẹn gặp lại.{See you next time!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:53.18,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, they were an energetic bunch!}Chà, mấy nhóc quậy ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.67,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Phải nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.62,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I don't think I wanna draw \NKyapicure for a while.}Em không muốn vẽ Kyapicure nữa đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.72,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You did draw a lot!}Em đã vẽ rất nhiều mà nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.43,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You're a star artist!}Nổi tiếng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.43,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What did you think, Shinozaki-san?}Em thấy sao Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:12.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Will today be useful for your proposal?}Có hữu dụng cho cuộc thi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's kind of vague, but I'm starting \Nto get a vision for what I want.}Tuy hơi mơ hồ nhưng em cũng hình dung ra rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.07,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll work hard so I can win \Nmost promising rookie!}Em sẽ cố hết sức ở giải tân binh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's the spirit!}Tinh thần được lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:26.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{By the way, do you think those two will be okay?}Cơ mà hai đứa nó sẽ ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You mean Marin-chan and Tomo-kun?}Marin và Tomo á?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{They had made up\Nby the time we were leaving.}Hình như hai đứa đã làm lành rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sure they'll be okay!}Chắc sẽ ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I think so, too.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.59,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If you like a girl, be nice to her.}Nếu thích ai thì phải tốt với họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Be nice to the girls you like...}Tốt với cô gái mình thích à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:56.69,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Shinozaki-san is always nice to me, isn't he?}Shinozaki lúc nào cũng dịu dàng với mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:21:00.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Is the cap stuck? I can open it for you.}Cứng lắm ạ? Để em mở cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.95,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Too hot? Let's turn the AC on.}Nóng ạ? Để em mở máy lạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So... so nice...}D-Dịu dàng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So nice!}Dịu dàng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.45,Sign_Basic,Window sign,0,0,0,,{\c&HD9C4A5&\b1\bord0\shad0\frz30.3\pos(145.334,115.333)}{Death By Nice}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.45,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai?!}C-Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are you okay, Senpai?! What's wrong?!}Chị ổn chứ? Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm okay.}Chị ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.07,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Adorable.}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Use my handkerchief!}Sử dụng khăn giấy của em nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.17,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:40.07,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.55,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:48.77,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.73,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:58.62,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:03.12,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:07.29,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:12.37,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:17.98,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:22.77,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:27.17,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:32.09,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:36.11,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:38.40,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.66,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby you're the sugar}
